title: Ross_Kemp_On_Gangs_-_EP03_-_Cape_Town_-_Numbers_Gang
description:
Episode 3 - Cape Town

Ross explores the country?s multifaceted Number?s Gang which thrives on the over-crowded prisons. In Pollsmoor Prison Ross experiences the terrifying sensation of incarceration among vicious murderers, rapists, and violent armed-robbers. He receives first hand accounts of the police killings which are required for initiation into the gang.
